Title: Honor and Tribute
Description:
It be time to return home. Let us welcome dese loa to the Echo Isles. Their positive influence should make short work of Mueh'zala's presence.

Go ahead, I be right behind ya.
ObjectivesText: Set up the loa altars at Darkspear Hold.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Tzadah in the Echo Isles.

Objectives.Text: Return to Echo Isles using Jani's Junkpile
